<plot>At Sciltre, nothing that is served up is what it seems and sometimes what you get isn't what you really want. When Simone agrees to a blind date with Oliver at the hottest restaurant in town, she doesn't have high expectations of the evening. She's not disappointed - Oliver turns out to be a nightmare. Seeking a mental escape, Simone begins to tune into what's happening with the other couples around her. With the help of the sulty Nina, sitting alone in the center of the restaurant, Simone gets caught up in the flirting, fighting and food and discovers that sometimes, the best things may not be on the menu.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104462</url></doc>
